divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside on my balcony in the sky were two orange lights I never seen anything like it in the sky, they moved very slow with no sound then about 15 mints later one orange light went out then the other light went out, I dont know where they went. In California lately we had a black out I seen the orange light again it came from the north in a flight pattern and turned east again no sound and moved slowly this time my family had seen this object I decided to tell someone because I want to let someone know what I seen I do believe this was a ufo also in the news this week someone has it on tape what they believe is a ufo Im not sure but the people talked about seeing the orange lights this sounded like what I seen two times before
